---
title: Elote-Style Corn & Potato Chowder with Cotija Cheese, Pepitas & Cilantro
description: Mexican street food inspired this creamy corn and potato chowder that's flavored with zingy garlic and smoky ancho chili powder, and topped with cotija cheese, cilantro, and pepitas. Best of all, these loaded bowls hit the table in a speedy 20 minutes for a warm and comforting main course that's perfect for any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67d7da1718d6e477003fc8ac-337d78fb.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67d7da1718d6e477003fc8ac-en-US.pdf
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/elote-style-corn-and-potato-chowder-67d7da1718d6e477003fc8ac
cuisine: Central America
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 670 kcal
  fat: 35 g
  saturated fat: 18 g
